snippet.title: LAURE X EKDEV LIMBU - TIHAR SONG [OFFICIAL VIDEO 2025] | KABITA NEPALI
snippet.description:
Actually, I created this song long time ago but whenever I listen to it, I felt something incomplete and I thought that I could do lot of experiments to make this song more close towards the perfection. This year, finally, with the help, courage and push from my beloved people I am able to present you guys this beautiful masterpiece. 

â€œTIHAR SONGâ€ is an occasional song but if you dissect this creation musically and visually, you can find lots of interesting things, which will make your normal days; lightened and brighten up like Tihar. snippet.description:
The biggest, spiciest ad film of the year is HERE! 
Atlee x Ranveer Singh team up with Sreeleela & Bobby Deol for the wildest cinematic explosion of action, drama, comedy & masala.

Watch the explosive trailer of AGENT CHING ATTACKS with jaw-dropping action, whistle-worthy drama, foot-tapping music, and masala so hotâ€¦ itâ€™ll set your screen on fire.

The full film premieres Sunday, October 19 exclusively on this channel.

WHAT TO EXPECT:
â€¢ Ranveer Singh in his most powerful avatar yet as Agent Ching
â€¢ Sreeleela adding spice and swagger as Agent Mirchi
â€¢ Bobby Deol unleashing chaos as Professor White Noise
â€¢ Signature Atlee scale, style & spectacle with a global A-list crew
â€¢ A brand-new version of the iconic anthem â€œMy Name is Ranveer Chingâ€

From Bhatinda to Beijing, thereâ€™s only one kingâ€¦ Ranveer Ching!

This is the BIGGEST celebration of Desi Chinese ever â€” bold, flavourful, cinematic, and guaranteed to #AagLagaDe.

About Chingâ€™s Secret - They say that to win Hindustani hearts even Chinese food became desi! And thereâ€™s only one Desi Chinese food brand that can make desi hearts beat faster â€“ Chingâ€™s. Saucy. Spicy. Sweet and sour. Hot and sour. Crunchy. Slurpy. Zesty. Schezwani. Manchurianâ€¦ Whatever be the kind of Desi Chinese your palate craves for, only Chingâ€™s can hit the spot with a perfect zing.

I â™¥ Desi Chinese!

nl-NL.description:
De grootste en meest pittige reclamefilm van het jaar is HIER!

Atlee x Ranveer Singh bundelen hun krachten met Sreeleela en Bobby Deol voor de wildste filmische explosie van actie, drama, komedie en masala.

Bekijk de explosieve trailer van AGENT CHING ATTACKS met adembenemende actie, fluitend drama, swingende muziek en masala zo heet... dat je scherm ervan in vuur en vlam staat.

De volledige film gaat op zondag 19 oktober exclusief op dit kanaal in premiÃ¨re.

WAT JE KUNT VERWACHTEN:
â€¢ Ranveer Singh in zijn krachtigste avatar tot nu toe als Agent Ching
â€¢ Sreeleela voegt pit en bravoure toe als Agent Mirchi
â€¢ Bobby Deol ontketent chaos als Professor White Noise
â€¢ De kenmerkende Atlee-schaal, stijl en spektakel met een wereldwijde A-lijst crew
â€¢ Een gloednieuwe versie van het iconische volkslied "My Name is Ranveer Ching"

Van Bhatinda tot Beijing, er is maar Ã©Ã©n koning... Ranveer Ching!

Dit is het GROOTSTE feest van Desi Chinees ooit â€” gedurfd, smaakvol, filmisch en gegarandeerd #AagLagaDe.

Over Ching's Secret - Ze zeggen dat zelfs Chinees eten desi werd om Hindoestaanse harten te veroveren! En er is maar Ã©Ã©n Desi Chinees merk dat desi harten sneller kan laten kloppen: Ching's. Pittig. Pittig. Zoetzuur. Pittig. Knapperig. Slurpend. Pittig. Manchurian... Wat voor soort Desi Chinees je smaakpapillen ook verlangen, alleen Ching's kan perfect smaken.

Film iklan terbesar dan terpedas tahun ini telah HADIR!
Atlee x Ranveer Singh berkolaborasi dengan Sreeleela & Bobby Deol untuk ledakan sinematik terliar yang memadukan aksi, drama, komedi, & masala.

About Creedence Clearwater Revival: 
Creedence Clearwater Revivalâ€™s 1968 self-titled debut album introduced the world to guitar-playing brothers John and Tomâ€¯Fogerty, drummer Doug Clifford, and bassist Stu Cook, four young men out of El Cerrito in the San Francisco Bay Area. Though they emerged in a place and time where trippy psychedelic visions were the order ofâ€¯the day, CCR bucked the trends and instead tapped into a rich, traditional seam of American music that connected to blues, country, rockabilly, gospel, folk and R&B.â€¯â€¯â€¯ 

During their short time together as a band (1968 â€“ 1972), the band enjoyed an unparalleled period of creativity lead by singer, songwriter, arranger John Fogerty. Theyâ€™ve sold close to 100 million records, releasing 14 Top 10 hits. They also managed to play over 150 tour dates around the world, including a headlining spot at Woodstock.

Creedence Clearwater Revivalâ€™s canon has become a part of the Great American Songbook. Fogerty penned songs like â€œBad Moon Rising,â€ â€œDown on the Corner,â€ â€œFortunate Son,â€ â€œHave You Ever Seen the Rain,â€ â€œProud Mary,â€ â€œBorn on the Bayou,â€ â€œTravelinâ€™ Bandâ€ and â€œUp Around the Bendâ€ have been ingrained into pop culture â€” not just as rock staples, but as classic standards.

With so many memorable songs that continue to grace our radio waves, television and movie screens, plus lyrics that still resonate today, Creedence Clearwater Revival is, truly, Americaâ€™s greatest rock â€™nâ€™ roll band.

snippet.title: Rs 50000 Minecraft DeathSwap Challenge with a YouTuber!
snippet.description:
Rs 50000 Minecraft DeathSwap Challenge with a YouTuber!


Instagram pe 50k kar do: https://www.instagram.com/psd_1/

In this video, I do a Minecraft deathswap challenge with my YouTuber friend @MrLapis 
where we both get 15 mins to build traps for each other, and as the timer finishes, our position gets swapped with each other. The player who survives in the end wins and gets Rs 50000!

Goddess Lakshmi Mata is the goddess of wealth, wisdom, prosperity, grace, generosity and charm.
